record.field:
Sent to customers on order confirmation.
Please do the following in the background of WeChat official account:
1. "Setting and development" → "official account setting" → "service category";
2. Add "Tools>Office" to the service category;
3. "Advertising Services and Services" → "Template Messages" → "Template Library" → "Category Template Library", search for "Sales Order Confirmed Notification";
4. Add template with number "59610"

Sent to customers when you cancel an order.
Please do the following in the background of WeChat official account:
1. "Setting and development" → "official account setting" → "service category";
2. Add "Tools>Office" to the service category;
3. "Advertising Services and Services" → "Template Messages" → "Template Library" → "Category Template Library", search for "Sales order cancelled notification";
4. Add template with number "59611"
